{"id":1066,"date":"2026-06-28T07:07:15","date_gmt":"2026-06-28T06:07:15","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/?st-import=5703b44157b42b600703943e40791d1a"},"modified":"2026-07-09T13:09:23","modified_gmt":"2026-07-09T12:09:23","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1066\" class=\"elementor elementor-1066\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c7ccba e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5c7ccba\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f2f473f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f2f473f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Me<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d83736 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2d83736\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d06618 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1d06618\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">My Story<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0572b54 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0572b54\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\">From a young age, I was always drawn to mathematics and physics, but what really sparked my interest in engineering was spending time working on cars with my dad. Whether it was understanding how different mechanical components worked or helping with repairs, I enjoyed seeing how individual parts came together to form a complete system. At the same time, I was fascinated by robotics and the possibilities it offered, which led me to pursue a degree in Robotics Engineering at Polytech Dijon after finishing high school.<\/p><p class=\"isSelectedEnd\">Over the past five years at Polytech Dijon, I have built a strong foundation in robotics through courses covering embedded systems, sensors, control, computer vision, automation, and robot programming. Alongside the theoretical aspects of the degree, we completed many practical projects that allowed us to apply what we had learned. These projects quickly became my favourite part of the course, as I enjoy tackling engineering challenges, finding practical solutions, and seeing ideas develop into working systems.<\/p><p class=\"isSelectedEnd\">During my studies, I also bought my first 3D printer. What initially started as a way to repair broken parts soon became a hobby of its own. As I became more confident using CAD software and additive manufacturing, I began designing my own parts and creating projects from scratch. One of the things I enjoy most is taking an idea from a sketch or concept and turning it into a functional object that solves a real problem.<\/p><p>My internships gave me the opportunity to apply everything I had learned at university while developing new technical and professional skills in an industrial environment. Working at Bosch Research in Germany and Singapore, as well as Schneider Electric in France, allowed me to collaborate with experienced engineers, work on real-world robotics and automation projects, and discover how engineering is carried out in international teams. Living and working abroad also strengthened my communication skills and gave me the opportunity to experience different cultures and ways of working.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c28b61b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c28b61b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">My Journey<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-53c636a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"53c636a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa575c6 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fa575c6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Europole_Logo.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1685\" alt=\"europole logo\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Europole_Logo.jpg 256w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Europole_Logo-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e2dfe9f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e2dfe9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2018 \u2013 2021<\/strong><br \/>French Baccalaur\u00e9at &amp; German Abitur<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ec37a7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9ec37a7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77727ad elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"77727ad\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/UB_and_Polytech_Dijon_Logos.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1682\" alt=\"ub and polytech dijon logos\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-105477a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"105477a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2021<\/strong><br \/>Began my Robotics Engineering degree at Polytech Dijon.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d939d78 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d939d78\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7b61617 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7b61617\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"410\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-1024x410.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1683\" alt=\"schneider electric logo\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-1024x410.png 1024w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-300x120.png 300w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-768x307.png 768w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-1536x615.png 1536w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/SCHNEIDER_ELECTRIC_logo-2048x820.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1202471 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1202471\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2024<\/strong><br \/>Engineering internship at Schneider Electric in Fontanil-Cornillon, France, working on industrial hardware and HMI development.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1128e85 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1128e85\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2cde571 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2cde571\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1024x640.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1684\" alt=\"bosch logo\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1024x640.png 1024w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-300x187.png 300w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-768x480.png 768w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1536x960.png 1536w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-2048x1280.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2efab6 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c2efab6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2025<\/strong><br \/>R&amp;D internship at Bosch Research in Renningen, Germany, developing prototypes for an autonomous mobile robot charging station and programming collaborative robots.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8dc6be7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8dc6be7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3582f16 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3582f16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1024x640.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1684\" alt=\"bosch logo\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1024x640.png 1024w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-300x187.png 300w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-768x480.png 768w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-1536x960.png 1536w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Bosch_Logo-2048x1280.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-505572d elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"505572d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2026<\/strong><br \/>R&amp;D internship at Bosch Research in Singapore, working on robot perception, ROS 2 integration, and AI-assisted engineering tools.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-95d20a0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"95d20a0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57c765a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"57c765a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-793889c elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"793889c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/forward-button.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1686\" alt=\"forward button\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/forward-button.png 512w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/forward-button-300x300.png 300w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/forward-button-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"  title=\"About\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92c9aca elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"92c9aca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f8bf69b elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f8bf69b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Today<\/strong><br \/>Looking forward to applying my skills to new engineering challenges while continuing to learn and grow.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e5891f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1e5891f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Outside Engineering<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6119d2a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6119d2a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\">Outside of engineering, I enjoy continuing to design and build things with my 3D printer, often creating practical solutions for everyday problems or exploring new ideas. I also enjoy running, playing badminton, and travelling. Living and working in France, Germany, and Singapore has given me the opportunity to experience different cultures and has strengthened both my adaptability and my appreciation for working in international teams.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b59fd2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6b59fd2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why This Portfolio?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f381e2b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f381e2b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer\" data-start=\"443\" data-end=\"883\">I created this portfolio to complement my CV by showcasing some of the projects that have shaped my engineering journey. It includes a selection of robotics projects completed during my studies, together with several 3D printing projects ranging from my very first designs, where I was learning CAD software and the fundamentals of additive manufacturing, to more complex designs where the main challenge was developing an effective solution.<\/p><p data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"1082\">Rather than presenting every project I have worked on, I chose those that best demonstrate how I approach engineering problems, learn new technologies, and develop ideas from concept to reality.<\/p><p data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"1082\">Looking back, that&#8217;s probably the common thread between all of my projects. Whether it&#8217;s a university robotics assignment, a prototype developed during an internship, or a part designed on my own 3D printer, what I enjoy most is taking an idea and turning it into something real. That&#8217;s exactly what I hope this portfolio conveys.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a562fae e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a562fae\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-abc8a60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion\" data-id=\"abc8a60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}\" data-widget_type=\"nested-accordion.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-n-accordion\" aria-label=\"Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-1800\" class=\"e-n-accordion-item\" >\n\t\t\t\t<summary class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title\" data-accordion-index=\"1\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-